==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hedonism
<hw>Hed"on*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
doctrine of the Hedonic sect; the pursuit of pleasure as a matter of
ethical principle.</def> <wns>[wns=1]</wns>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The ethical theory which finds the explanation and
authority of duty in its tendency to give pleasure.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hedonist</ent>⟦br⟧
